originalText.text: No 1 hr parking its 3 hr for 30 $ after that price increased. Sayin this cuz someone in the review said 10$ an hour. I mean technically its 10$ an hour but its like u gotta pay for 3 hr even if u get out early

originalText.text:
My suggestion to you. If you have to park somewhere, there are plenty of parking around this area try to not park here. Some of the people are rude, others are can't speak a word of english. And if you're a monthly parker here like myself ...keep an eye on your car or put a camera in there...you most likely will have something taken from your car in some form.

I had a charger that was supposed  to be for my car battery and coming to get something from my car someone (probably one of the employees) ransacked my car and  took my charger and feigned ignorance as if they didn't know what happened. But i've noticed i've been missing a couple of things and somethings replaced in my car that i've NEVER placed in!!

and for some reason, they keep the windows down so that ANYONE can go into your car! its crazy!!

At this point, if you parked here via monthly I suggest you take a look into your car and if anything report this place. Or look elsewhere!
